{"tid":1492031,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"要結婚，但呢排同屋企人關係唔好","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T03:38:04.000Z","uid":2459,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"48e5692a1d9dd912d0dda3aee5791628c9df4108","tid":1492031,"uid":2459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:55:42.000Z","msg":"年頭求左婚，決定下年結婚<br />\n諗住雙方家長見左面先至擇日<br />\n由5月話見，拖到8月都未夾到時間<br />\n<br />\n宜家另一伴話唔想再拖，想快啲搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係呢幾個月既事我已經老母嘈到反哂面<br />\n（我老母企得好硬，嘈到話要同我割蓆）<br />\n搞到連見都唔駛見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜野都傾唔到<br />\n但我地認為點都要食餐飯見下面<br />\n<br />\n無理由淨係預老豆唔預老母<br />\n但以我老母性格一係唔去一係就閪哂面<br />\n究竟我應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343d5e11412d9b764ddbfa1da843d0aca0ba904b","tid":1492031,"uid":16061,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:57:52.000Z","msg":"淨係簽紙 通知佢一聲結左婚<br />\n完"},{"pid":"b5c3e0d7ed4bcaa5d25db384b49167e0dce2ce79","tid":1492031,"uid":28244,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:58:48.000Z","msg":"咁既老母 講聲 去咪去唔去咪唔去 唔好同佢嘈 到時佢後悔係佢自己唔黎 你有邀請過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係佢放棄機會"},{"pid":"f81e185fd93cd0dd07d1f839b1a26a33222e948b","tid":1492031,"uid":152040,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:59:17.000Z","msg":"咩事同你老母關係唔好？"},{"pid":"931fb8f1ff73068b39d80cd9ed8b6e9875439d26","tid":1492031,"uid":2562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019